---
import WikiLayout from '../layouts/WikiLayout.astro';
import TableOfContents from '../components/TableOfContents.astro';
import InfoBox from '../components/InfoBox.astro';

const pageTitle = "Welcome to Shoppis Wiki";

// These would typically come from a content management system or markdown files
const headings = [
  { depth: 2, slug: "about-shopis", text: "About Shopis" },
  { depth: 2, slug: "getting-started", text: "Getting Started" },
  { depth: 2, slug: "how-to-use-this-wiki", text: "How to Use This Wiki" },
  { depth: 2, slug: "key-features", text: "Key Features" },
];
---

<WikiLayout title={pageTitle}>
  <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">{pageTitle}</h1>
    <div class="flex gap-2">
      <a href="#" class="text-sm px-3 py-1 border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 rounded-md text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 hover:bg-neutral-50 dark:hover:bg-neutral-800">
        View history
      </a>
      <a href="#" class="text-sm px-3 py-1 border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 rounded-md text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 hover:bg-neutral-50 dark:hover:bg-neutral-800">
        Discussion
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <TableOfContents headings={headings} />

  <InfoBox type="info" title="Wiki Status">
    This wiki is continuously updated with the latest information about Shoppis. Last updated: January 2025.
  </InfoBox>

  <h2 id="about-shoppis">About Shoppis</h2>
  <p>
    Shoppis is an innovative shopping list and grocery management application designed to streamline your shopping experience. 
    Launched in 2024, Shoppis combines cutting-edge technology with intuitive design to help users create, manage, and share 
    shopping lists efficiently.
  </p>
  <p>
    With features like voice recognition, barcode scanning, and smart notifications, Shoppis transforms the traditional 
    shopping list into a powerful tool for budget management, meal planning, and collaborative shopping. Whether you're 
    shopping for groceries, planning meals, or managing household supplies, Shoppis adapts to your lifestyle.
  </p>

  <h2 id="getting-started">Getting Started</h2>
  <p>
    New to Shoppis? This section will help you understand the basics of using the application and its key features.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/getting-started/what-is-shoppis">What is Shoppis?</a> - An overview of the application and its purpose</li>
    <li><a href="/getting-started/introduction">Introduction</a> - Getting familiar with Shoppis</li>
    <li><a href="/getting-started/user-interface-overview">User Interface Overview</a> - Navigate the app with confidence</li>
    <li><a href="/user-guide/create-an-account">Create an Account</a> - Step-by-step guide to setting up your Shoppis account</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="how-to-use-this-wiki">How to Use This Wiki</h2>
  <p>
    This wiki is organized into several main sections, each focusing on different aspects of Shoppis:
  </p>
  <ol>
    <li><strong>Getting Started</strong> - Basic information for new users</li>
    <li><strong>User Guide</strong> - Detailed instructions for using Shoppis features</li>
    <li><strong>Features</strong> - In-depth explanations of Shoppis's capabilities</li>
    <li><strong>Shopping Insights</strong> - Analytics and reporting features</li>
    <li><strong>Technical</strong> - Technical specifications and API documentation</li>
  </ol>
  <p>
    You can navigate through these sections using the sidebar on the left. Each page includes a table of contents 
    to help you find specific information quickly.
  </p>

  <InfoBox type="success" title="Quick Tip">
    Use the search function at the top of the page to quickly find specific topics across the entire wiki.
  </InfoBox>

  <h2 id="key-features">Key Features</h2>
  <p>
    Shoppis offers a variety of features designed to enhance your shopping and planning experience:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Voice Recognition</strong> - Add items to your list using voice commands</li>
    <li><strong>Barcode Scanner</strong> - Quickly add products by scanning their barcodes</li>
    <li><strong>Smart Notifications</strong> - Get reminders and suggestions based on your shopping patterns</li>
    <li><strong>List Sharing</strong> - Collaborate with family and friends on shared shopping lists</li>
    <li><strong>Purchase Tracking</strong> - Monitor your spending and track purchase history</li>
    <li><strong>Planning Assistant</strong> - AI-powered meal planning and shopping suggestions</li>
    <li><strong>Cross-Device Sync</strong> - Access your lists from any device, anywhere</li>
    <li><strong>Budget Goals</strong> - Set and track spending goals with detailed analytics</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    Explore the wiki to learn more about these features and how to make the most of your Shoppis experience.
  </p>
</WikiLayout>
